{"tid":1541874,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」 全民演唱會不是夢","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T09:06:50.000Z","uid":201266,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9175d29407d56c6d1ca8d95b441c13311f883812","tid":1541874,"uid":201266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"在場寶寶可以一齊唱喎❤️<br />\n<br />\n【虐殺市民】（聖誕老人）<br />\n虐殺市民 終身監禁<br />\n陀住支槍去殺人<br />\n見到令妹 起勢卜棍<br />\n賭波飲茶 實幫襯<br />\n<br />\n【有班警察毅進仔】（有隻雀仔跌落水）<br />\n有班警察毅進仔<br />\n人又廢 又要威<br />\n有班警察位置低<br />\n做狗乞米<br />\n<br />\n【亂咁打人】（打開蚊帳）<br />\n亂咁打人 亂咁打人<br />\n亂棍扑 亂棍扑<br />\n記者都要打埋 訓低都照打埋<br />\n冇皇法 冇皇法<br />\n<br />\n【全犯法】（刷牙歌）<br />\n你被塔 佢被塔<br />\n香港警察全垃圾<br />\n小童成人全被塔<br />\n老人殘疾都應塔<br />\n<br />\n你被殺 佢被殺<br />\n差佬攞炮胡亂殺<br />\n青年兒童全射殺<br />\n警棍胡椒加膠彈<br />\n<br />\n【無自信】（硬漢子）<br />\n無自信 毅進仔<br />\n射炮博出位<br />\n人又廢 做隻龜<br />\n打人勁契弟<br />\n亂吠 冇得贊<br />\n成隊去打後生仔<br />\n亂射 太多發<br />\n樓上叫我再準啲"},{"pid":"02002fdceab911079b1fb57161e3a7f8dbea20e6","tid":1541874,"uid":270323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3153437a53f0a825722f6d62999de3f22152ce7b","tid":1541874,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"地方的狗宿需要大聲公"},{"pid":"23d69e61424d97dd968e0086dbde9b99f6d7696a","tid":1541874,"uid":74888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"願榮歸香港呀仲有！！"},{"pid":"4f1565d8d7bc3849a052b865f350b3d96b04e05b","tid":1541874,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-