e=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58a28017e015d22ffd9dbb95cd23100dc0f63bab","tid":1541874,"uid":6741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"童謠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba45d49e44d2bf72f0925e5729e1344c39d0760c","tid":1541874,"uid":108359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"點解冇何家仆街何家猜<br />\n<br />\n何家仆街何家猜<br />\n何家子孫何仆街<br />\n何家仆街何家猜<br />\n何家母親墳倒了 <br />\n南邊叔父何先生<br />\n同班黑幫齊嘻哈<br />\n酬金不足煩媽媽<br />\n娘親墳起了"},{"pid":"eb042664d230bee2ffd90c0e49065db14fa905f9","tid":1541874,"uid":201266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba45d49e44d2bf72f0925e5729e1344c39d0760c","tid":1541874,"uid":108359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"點解冇何家仆街何家猜<br />\n<br />\n何家仆街何家猜<br />\n何家子孫何仆街<br />\n何家仆街何家猜<br />\n何家母親墳倒了 <br />\n南邊叔父何先生<br />\n同班黑幫齊嘻哈<br />\n酬金不足煩媽媽<br />\n娘親墳起了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d93031706dd46c131b864d3164788021f8069d","tid":1541874,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:42:58.000Z",